<tr>
<th style="text-align:left"><em>Section Summary</em>  Monsters that need to harm humans to sustain themselves began to struggle and die off in the modern age as human society became more sophisticated. Includes vampires, succubi, and other demons and ghouls.  The Infernal Alliance was formed as a desperate attempt to find strength in numbers. Experiments were conducted using their combined magics, eventually leading to the creation of a new creature; the Somnivore.  Somnivores’ ability to feed on dreams without the need to harm their prey would allow their demonic heritage to live on and prosper, even in modern times. Reverie is a new realm that somnivores created. It lies parallel to Earth, providing ample space for their species to grow while maintaining easy access to their food source.</th>
